{"tid":2192965,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★零成本回血！Bauhaus員工離職被指「欠鐘」，需扣2,800元 愈滾愈大欠下「周身債」","createTime":"2020-09-07T12:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:49:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":114,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"ceac4765a868062aecba5f9e73fd869c5fd6dd25","tid":2192965,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"近日服裝品牌Bauhaus被指使用「負鐘」制度，變相剋扣員工的薪金假期。早前有員工在網上表示，在疫情之下公司縮短分店營業時間，惟每周合約時數維持不變，員工即使按照編更返齊工，仍不免硬食「負鐘」，愈滾愈大欠下「周身債」。當中有人離職時被指欠下51個小時，需扣2,800元薪金。<br />\n<br />\n隨着大批員工在Bauhaus官方專頁留言控訴，今日有網民發現，Bauhaus及集團旗下多個品牌的Facebook專頁已被刪除。職工盟透露，至今收到十多宗求助，又指雖然Bauhaus分別獲得零售業資助計劃和保就業計劃的資助，但近月有員工表示被公司解僱。組織除了批評其處理態度和手法，亦質疑Bauhaus有濫用補貼之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/520702/bauhaus%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E8%BF%94%E8%B6%B3%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%8D%E6%AC%A0-%E8%B2%A0%E9%90%98-%E5%82%B5-%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E9%9C%80%E6%89%A3%E8%96%AA%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F520702%2Fbauhaus%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25BF%2594%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%25AC%25A0-%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%2590%2598-%25E5%2582%25B5-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2581%25B7%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%2589%25A3%25E8%2596%25AA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E4%25BE%258B&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpxA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=448d43dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/520702/bauhaus%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E8%BF%94%E8%B6%B3%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%8D%E6%AC%A0-%E8%B2%A0%E9%90%98-%E5%82%B5-%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E9%9C%80%E6%89%A3%E8%96%AA%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B</a>"},{"pid":"ec670a4882df100573d0748ab320ab79b390f0ca","tid":2192965,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmo